{"tid":27341,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得曹操真係好勁","createTime":"2016-12-07T09:27:19.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T05:58:37.000Z","uid":28726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"20bcd8265e6179d919f7fab8d5a0918502cbcb3c","tid":27341,"uid":28726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T09:27:19.000Z","msg":"打仗嗰時勇武就人人皆知啦<br />\n<br />\n但其實佢啲文學才華都不容小覷<br />\n對後世影響好深嘅「建安風骨」嘅代表人物就係曹操<br />\n佢生啲仔又勁<br />\n例如曹植係建安風骨嘅最具代表性人物<br />\n<br />\n曹操真係文武雙全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43cc0f43c5ae81294649b7306bf6dfaacc7959c","tid":27341,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T09:45:11.000Z","msg":"覺  比三國演義抹黑晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aae9a7d55736e93adb2dff0f9bc36e1ffceb43e","tid":27341,"uid":27652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T09:49:43.000Z","msg":"覺 你見有咁多勁人幫佢就知佢有料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33716a034f912e4217998a4a9e16b640d11f443b","tid":27341,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:02:37.000Z","msg":"覺"},{"pid":"7f1202f507478d589c78e5c55700737207400bf9","tid":27341,"uid":48214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:05:05.000Z","msg":"再勁都過唔到幾多代就比晉ko左"},{"pid":"0154c37ef4fc1f810860dcc16f41639f501ef24a","tid":27341,"uid":28726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:34:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺  比三國演義抹黑晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n羅生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f71c6e4deb1ac5af1eadcef9ebc58c1da5f146d3","tid":27341,"u