r />\n自己攻 又 打唔win<br />\n<br />\n自己家事又係一塌糊塗 仲搞到要賜死洛神"},{"pid":"edf6447fe73710637a7fbe4a1097fbbb8b6adcc9","tid":27341,"uid":39862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T08:27:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>再勁都過唔到幾多代就比晉ko左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嚴格黎講唔係<br />\n曹操一生都冇諗過稱帝/創新朝代<br />\n魏亡於司馬氏<br />\n嚴格黎講唔關佢事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嚴格黎講 魏係曹丕建國<br />\n司馬懿係曹丕封相<br />\n其實完全唔關曹操事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458d049b8d50fcfa8fc2c5581cfa22a0065eb6f7","tid":27341,"uid":4249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T08:40:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/09/164006_dc8f2d269863eba995afa59e681c287f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F09%2F164006_dc8f2d269863eba995afa59e681c287f.jpg&h=bd35c10a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一睇就知勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"033411300e4197b45412f8ff8515bcd9d18d0274","tid":27341,"uid":36724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T08:42:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>&lt;blockquote&gt;再勁都過唔到幾多代就比晉ko左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n嚴格黎講唔係<br />\n曹操一生都冇諗過稱帝/創新朝代<br />\n魏亡於司馬氏<br />\n嚴格黎講唔關佢事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢最後幾年清算好多支持漢室的大臣，同扶值支持曹家的人，為的係等佢個仔做皇帝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而司馬仲達同佢做的野一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14f6455bbcda8608d77f2e7bc926c6b8be9fc189","tid":27341,"uid":38684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T11:03:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>再勁都過唔到幾多代就比晉ko左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嚴格黎講唔係<br />\n曹操一生都冇諗過稱帝/創新朝代<br />\n魏亡於司馬氏<br />\n嚴格黎講唔關佢事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嚴格黎講 魏係曹丕建國<br />\n司馬懿係曹丕封相<br />\n其實完全唔關曹操事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢最醒就係乾手淨腳<br />\n終一生<br />\n最後都擺明做亂臣賊子<br />\n當然從佢後期疏遠荀彧等主張復漢派<br />\n一事都可知<br />\n其實佢有不臣之心<br />\n至少佢冇當過漢室係一回事"},{"pid":"cf83a047e483356c4a014af8dac6624243b68df4","tid":27341,"uid":38684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T11:05:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>再勁都過唔到幾多代就比晉ko左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁又係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嚴格黎講唔係<br />\n曹操一生都冇諗過稱帝/創新朝代<br />\n魏亡於司馬氏<br />\n嚴格黎講唔關佢事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢最後幾年清算好多支持漢室的大臣，同扶值支持曹家的人，為的係等佢個仔做皇帝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而司馬仲達同佢做的野一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實佢晚期都知兩個仔都叮噹馬頭<br />\n自己唔搞一定會打到你死我活<br />\n自己快手收一邊至少唔使內鬥先<br />\n但係揀曹丕就真係唔知有咩好<br />\n最好其實係曹昂<br />\n不過晨早死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"070be0d6fbdd50ab9a128c680237105f4278a444","tid":27341,"uid":38684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T11:11:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係死係唔識教仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n張繡，于禁的處理 呢d唔好講<br />\n<br />\n小氣 私怨極大  <br />\n例1 好像曹洪唔肯借錢 搞度自己老母求佢<br />\n例2 上位後將支持曹植果d殺哂 例丁氏兄弟<br />\n<br />\n朋黨為患  識埋d咩人 代表佢人格都好極有限公司<br />\n果堆咩孟達 司馬懿 吳質 陳群 呢個圈<br />\n一個 死後叛國(孟達) 一個死後奪國(司馬懿隔多代)<br />\n<br />\n向士族 全面投降 <br />\n九品中正制唔好講<br />\n<br />\n佢自己又like打獵 圈地 同佢玩建築個仔<br />\n2個有穩定的大北方 搞內政都差強人意<br />\n<br />\n戰略眼光差 已經唔駛講<br />\n好像當年劉曄 叫攻吳 唔攻<br />\n自己攻 又 打唔win<br />\n<br />\n自己家事又係一塌糊塗 仲搞到要賜死洛神</blockquote><br />\n佢內政好差咩<br />\n佢都改人頭稅做戶調制<br />\n又搞番屯田制同改善水利<br />\n其實都有重要貢獻<br />\n家事就真係搞唔掂<br />\n搞自己新抱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}